    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078030/extras/3cfd8e6edc724ad727cea5018af02f90.poster.avif?t=1753252500\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078030/extras/3cfd8e6edc724ad727cea5018af02f90.webm?t=1753252500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078030/extras/3cfd8e6edc724ad727cea5018af02f90.mp4?t=1753252500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roguelike、塔防自动战斗游戏。</strong><br>召唤亡者、对抗骑士，并操控先进的未来无人机舰队，在这个战略战斗模拟器中穿越各个时代展开激战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级你的基地，解锁新科技，在敌人升级之前将其摧毁。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078030/extras/f57fc9a49af9b433605559744149e241.poster.avif?t=1753252500\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078030/extras/f57fc9a49af9b433605559744149e241.webm?t=1753252500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078030/extras/f57fc9a49af9b433605559744149e241.mp4?t=1753252500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>核心特色：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>跨越时代进化：</strong><br>从刀剑与盾牌起步，逐步发展到激光与无人机，适应不断变化的战场环境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>指挥与征服：</strong><br>合理布置防御工事，升级武器装备，智取狡猾的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式美术风格：</strong><br>鲜明的卡通渲染风格让丰富多变的战场栩栩如生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快节奏战斗：</strong><br>在战术决策与战斗混乱之间寻找平衡。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078030/extras/61d06265f191a779ff6ef88afd108c13.poster.avif?t=1753252500\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078030/extras/61d06265f191a779ff6ef88afd108c13.webm?t=1753252500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078030/extras/61d06265f191a779ff6ef88afd108c13.mp4?t=1753252500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级你的主基地，添加炮塔，占领据点，构筑坚固防线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握适应之道，在瞬息万变的战场中赢得胜利。无论是守卫破败废墟，还是掌控未来科技，每一个决策都将引领你征服整个时代。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078030/extras/83c66c34ee958c188a6d602f5d8eccd7.poster.avif?t=1753252500\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078030/extras/83c66c34ee958c188a6d602f5d8eccd7.webm?t=1753252500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078030/extras/83c66c34ee958c188a6d602f5d8eccd7.mp4?t=1753252500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
